{
  "texts": [
    "We use the SGD optimizer with a momentum of 0.9, a weight decay of 1 × 10 -3, and batch size of 32.",
    "We train the network for 10 epochs with learning rate 1 × 10 -3 and 1 × 10 -4 for 5 epochs each.",
    "Typical data augmentations including random horizontal flip are applied.For ISIC-2017, we follow the experimental setting in previous work [53], [54].",
    "For preprocessing, we use 2000 training images and 600 test images, all resized to 256 × 256 and augmented with random mirroring, flipping, and gamma transformations, as described in [54].",
    "We use nnU-Net [55] as a segmentation network."
  ]
}